Package: nlmixr2llm
Title: LLM Instructions for the 'nlmixr2' Pharmacometrics Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "John", family = "Harrold",
                  email = "john.m.harrold@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Ships agent and skill documentation that helps large language
    models write correct code for the 'nlmixr2' pharmacometrics ecosystem
    ('rxode2', 'nlmixr2', 'nonmem2rx', 'monolix2rx', 'babelmixr2'). Provides
    accessor functions to use the content as a system prompt with any large
    language model client (e.g., the 'ellmer' package) and installer functions
    that write the content into the conventions expected by Claude Code, OpenAI
    Codex CLI, Positron Assistant, and other tools that read 'AGENTS.md'.
License: BSD_3_clause + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/john-harrold/nlmixr2llm, https://john-harrold.github.io/nlmixr2llm/
BugReports: https://github.com/john-harrold/nlmixr2llm/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    tools,
    utils
